 Killed about 10,000 people, 

00:03:39.149 --> 00:03:43.846
 Most of them belonged to the three countries in West Africa. 

00:03:43.846 --> 00:03:46.433
 There are three reasons why the epidemic may not spread further. 

00:03:46.433 --> 00:03:50.874
 The first reason is due to the heroic work done by health workers. 

00:03:50.874 --> 00:03:54.136
 They treat people and prevent more cases. 

00:03:54.136 --> 00:03:56.621
 The second is the nature of the virus. 

00:03:56.621 --> 00:03:59.697
 Ebola does not spread through the air. 

00:03:59.697 --> 00:04:01.810
 When the disease reaches the stage of infection, 

00:04:01.810 --> 00:04:04.550
 Most of the infected people are in bed. 

00:04:06.590 --> 00:04:10.411
 Third, the epidemic has not entered many urban areas. 

00:04:10.411 --> 00:04:12.115
 That was just luck. 

00:04:12.115 --> 00:04:14.355
 If he entered urban areas, 

00:04:14.355 --> 00:04:17.877
 The numbers would have been much greater. 

00:04:17.877 --> 00:04:21.466
 So next time, we may not be very lucky. 

