 First, we need strong health systems in poor countries. 

00:06:20.591 --> 00:06:23.778
 Mothers can give birth safely, 

00:06:23.778 --> 00:06:25.295
 And children have access to all vaccines. 

00:06:25.295 --> 00:06:29.634
 He was also able to reveal the beginning of the epidemic early. 

